<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/apr/06/">&#x27a0;</a> April 6, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="advanced_access_content_system" >

        
        <a name="002370"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.lotspiech.com/AACS/">Advanced Access Content System</a></h4>

        

        <p>An overview of how the AACS encryption system that&#8217;ll be baked into Bluray and HD-DVD works.  It&#8217;s very well-crafted, but ultimately doomed-to-fail &#8212; either through cracking, or through speedy product-obsolescence.</p>

